# Cyber Platform Lab

A technical cybersecurity laboratory bringing together practical projects covering Cloud Security, DevSecOps, Detection Engineering, Kubernetes Security and Secrets Management.

This repository documents a coherent engineering approach for designing, securing, monitoring and continuously improving modern infrastructures.

---

## About

The objective of this laboratory is to consolidate the technical skills developed throughout my cybersecurity curriculum by reproducing environments representative of those encountered in industry.

Each module focuses on a specific domain while remaining part of a single security architecture.

The repository is organised to reflect a complete security lifecycle:

- Secure infrastructure provisioning
- Secure software delivery
- Container and Kubernetes security
- Detection engineering and monitoring
- Secrets management

Rather than presenting isolated demonstrations, the projects are designed to illustrate how these technologies complement one another within a modern cybersecurity environment.

